Class XslResolver

java.lang.Object
  com.rexsl.core.XslResolver
All Implemented Interfaces:
ContextResolver<Marshaller>
@Provider
public final class XslResolver
extends Object
implements ContextResolver<Marshaller>

Provider of JAXB Marshaller for JAX-RS framework.

You don't need to use this class directly. It is made public only becuase JAX-RS implementation should be able to discover it in classpath.
